    <div class="ublp2-faq__inner">
      <span class="ublp2-eyebrow">— FAQ</span>
      <h2 class="ublp2-h2">Common <em>questions.</em></h2>
      <details class="ublp2-faq__item">
        <summary>How does UBurn actually work?<span class="ublp2-faq__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
        <div class="ublp2-faq__body">Glucomannan, a soluble konjac fiber, forms a natural gel when it meets water in your stomach. EFSA recognizes this mechanism for satiety support within an energy-controlled diet. Result: you feel satisfied for up to 4 hours after one scoop.*</div>
      </details>
      <details class="ublp2-faq__item">
        <summary>When will I notice a difference?<span class="ublp2-faq__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
        <div class="ublp2-faq__body">Most customers report satiety from the first scoop. For consistent control over afternoon cravings, 7–14 days of daily use produces the most reliable signal.*</div>
      </details>
      <details class="ublp2-faq__item">
        <summary>Does it contain caffeine?<span class="ublp2-faq__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
        <div class="ublp2-faq__body">Zero caffeine. UBurn is built on plant fibers and natural actives — no jitters, no afternoon crash, drinkable any time of day.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="ublp2-faq__item">
        <summary>How does it taste?<span class="ublp2-faq__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
        <div class="ublp2-faq__body">Hazelnut-vanilla notes. Smooth, naturally violet color from purple ube root. Mix with cold water, oat milk, or hot frothed milk depending on your moment.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="ublp2-faq__item">
        <summary>Subscribe or one-time?<span class="ublp2-faq__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
        <div class="ublp2-faq__body">Both. Subscribe & save gives −10% + free bonuses. You can pause, skip or cancel anytime from your account. No lock-in.</div>
      </details>
    </div>
  </section>

